### Get all students
GET http://localhost:3000/students
Accept: application/json

### Create a student
POST http://localhost:3000/students
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Alice",
  "lastName": "Mwangi",
  "email": "alice.mwangi@example.com",
  "age": 20,
  "gender": "Female",
  "level": "Undergraduate",
  "phone": "0788000123",
  "address": "Kigali, Rwanda"
}

### Get all teachers
GET http://localhost:3000/teachers
Accept: application/json

### Create a teacher
POST http://localhost:3000/teachers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "department": "Mathematics",
  "hireDate": "2015-09-01",
  "phone": "0788123456",
  "office": "B201"
}

### Update a student (replace id)
PUT http://localhost:3000/students/<REPLACE_STUDENT_ID>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "level": "Graduate"
}

### Delete a teacher (replace id)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/teachers/<REPLACE_TEACHER_ID>
